banner.title: Al-Qatarya
banner.desc: Al-Qataria Company provides a trained and distinguished group of technicians to provide the highest levels of high technology in the shortest possible time
services.top.desc: We work with you to enhance the durability of your projects... Engineering Company for Trade and Supplies
services.top-feature-1.desc: We specialize in thermal insulation works for buildings, industrial facilities and all major projects.
services.top-feature-2.desc: We specialize in waterproofing works for buildings, industrial facilities and all major projects.
services.top-feature-3.desc: We specialize in fireproofing works for buildings, industrial facilities and all major projects.
services.top-feature-4.desc: We specialize in soundproofing works for buildings, industrial facilities and all major projects.
services-desc: We appreciate the importance of work, and our company is distinguished by its honesty, quality, and high level among its competitors. The work team is trained to the highest level and has experience in performing work and home maintenance.
projects-desc: The latest insulation projects throughout Qatar
why.us-desc: Our management works to enhance the construction of projects according to modern technologies
why.us-paragraph: Trust is built with our customers and in its various sectors without competition, and this is what we always see in your eyes and your level of satisfaction. We contribute with you to developing your facilities and work together to satisfy your customers. We are keen to carry out your work without any defects, as we have cadres of highly qualified engineers and technicians that achieve your desired successes.
who.we.are-desc: Get to know our team members and our workplace
who.we.are-paragraph: For more than 30 years, the engineering company has prepared a team that is considered one of the most skilled engineers and technicians in Egypt in the field of insulation, its modern technologies, and extensive training programs to always provide what is best.
partners-desc: An overview of the most important completed projects and the opinions of our customers
planning: Start planning your insulation project today...
planning-desc: With early planning and before implementing your project for all types of insulation, contact our engineering team to obtain the best insulation materials for amazing and undoubted results... We work together to achieve your goals
footer.about-text: - All water and thermal insulation works for all types of surfaces - Insulating swimming pools and lakes - Insulating against fire - Insulating floors against chemicals and corrosion - Sound insulation
footer.support-text: Technical support is available to help you from 9 am to 7 pm
footer.address-text: Second Industrial Zone - 10th of Ramadan - Sharkia
who.we.are-paragraph1: An institution with extensive experience in the field of thermal insulation and water insulation in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia, including...
who.we.are-paragraph2: A trained technical team, an organized administrative body, and modern equipment and machines.
who.we.are-paragraph3: General activity: maintenance and operation of buildings - installation, repair and maintenance of heat, water and sound insulation systems - construction of concrete buildings - maintenance and operation of precast buildings.
who.we.are-paragraph4: Specialization: Specialized in supplying, implementing and repairing all water and thermal insulation systems and concrete repair.
who.we.are-paragraph5: The organization was able to gain the trust of its customers after completing the projects assigned to it to the fullest extent, and it is working to increase its resources and use modern technologies in order to complete the implementation of all required projects with the same high quality and accuracy while adhering to security and safety standards.
who.we.are-paragraph6: The organization enjoys great trust with customers, great accuracy in implementation and punctuality. It is keen to satisfy its customers and strive to gain the trust of more customers.
our.team-paragraph: The ETS Engineering Company team includes one hundred employees of engineers, technicians and professional workers to carry out various insulation works and possesses all the scientific and practical expertise. The projects are implemented after the engineering team receives consultation requests and makes a field visit to begin a comprehensive study of the project and all its requirements. Solutions are then provided along with the provision of samples on On the ground so that companies can park on it in the required manner and without significant defects.
about.us-desc: We contribute with you to the safety of your projects and the satisfaction of your customers is the satisfaction of achieving our goals of development with you.
vision-desc: We aim to be pioneers in the field of water and thermal insulation within the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia. With the expansion of the field to include the opening of several exhibitions for water and thermal insulation materials and equipment, in cooperation with the largest petrochemical factories such as Henkel, Pacific, and Huntsman companies, and equipment companies such as the American Graco and the Spanish Gamma, within the cities of the Kingdom.
mission-desc: We always strive to implement our projects in accordance with international quality standards, on time, in the optimal manner and in accordance with industry principles. We seek to achieve a comprehensive engineering renaissance in all areas of our work to achieve leadership in the field of thermal and water insulation. We seek to gain the greatest possible trust from customers and are committed to their satisfaction through adherence to accuracy, quality and safety standards and the use of technologies and professional work teams to implement all projects.
